Class ExecutionRequest

    • com.smartthings.sdk.smartapp.core.models.ExecutionRequest

public class ExecutionRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    The root model for all executions. An execution request is compositional in nature. Client's can expect exactly one *Data field set depending on the type of execution. For example, if execution is of type EVENT, the \"eventData\" field will be set.
